thread.title_full: Skipper (formerly Jetaport) reviewed by Sarah Montgomery

author: Sarah Montgomery
title: Sarah Montgomery
text: Great service! Needed to set up a group block for a party I'm hosting in another state. Was able to choose hotels that were best for my needs and got two great blocks for my guests to choose from. Erik was very thorough!
